channel.title: WTF how can i log in?
channel.description:
[b]if i log in it says this:
Error conecting to server. Must be down click ''Cancel'' then ''Start server'' to make your own.
but can i log in to other peeps than and were can i see what my server IP is :confused:[/b]
please reply this topic :)

item.title: WTF how can i log in?
item.dc:creator: @eambo eambo
item.description:
@eambo wrote:

If it’s YOUR server, running on you’re computer, it will always be 127.0.0.1 to connect to it.

If other people want to connect, go to www.ipchicken.com and find out you’re ip, and give it to them. YOU DO NOT USE THIS IP. YOU USE 127.0.0.1. THIS IP IS FOR OTHER PEOPLE TO CONNECT just had to emphasise that =-P
